WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'MyTiles' is a game where you try to clear boards filled with
numbered tiles. The game idea is to find a numbered tile that
matches the 'Next tile', located at the right in the window. Once
the tile is found, a new tile is displayed and so on, until the
entire game board is cleared.

  Sounds simple? Maybe, but there's a catch: some tiles are
stacked one above another, so there are many tiles that are hidden
under the visible ones and you must choose which one you will
select. Because if you select a wrong one and a particular tile,
that you will have to find after, is not visible at the time, the
game is over...
 
  Have fun!

